snippet.title: CodeParade
snippet.description: Welcome to Code Parade!  This is where I'll upload interesting projects and experiments that I do for fun.  Topics will usually involve machine learning, games, algorithms, fractals, or any other topics I find interesting.  I usually include some explanations, and sometimes tutorials.  If you have any ideas for projects, especially machine learning ones, feel free to post them on my channel discussion page!
